678
00:35:51,450 --> 00:35:52,340
Suzhou?

679
00:35:55,630 --> 00:35:58,360
Zhen, isa ka talagang buhay na imortal.

680
00:35:59,280 --> 00:36:02,070
Puro peke ang mga negosyanteng ibinigay sa amin ni Tiya.

681
00:36:02,110 --> 00:36:03,370
Hindi nga sila umiiral.

682
00:36:04,070 --> 00:36:05,280
At nalaman ko rin

683
00:36:05,730 --> 00:36:07,540
